title: Nozoki Ana (Official Colored)
description: Tatsuhiro moved to Tokyo to attend an art school and start his new life. In his new room, there’s a small hole in the wall. At first he can see nothing through the small hole, but one night, through the peeping hole, he saw a girl. That’s how his new life starts.

altTitles.ja: ノ・ゾ・キ・ア・ナ　フルカラー
